<10_4 /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Вот и все! <delay20 />Чистая правда!</message>
	<message label="Surprised" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="3" />! Показать тебе
